<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.8.6">
<l>porokkap paṉṉiyip pūmip poṟaitīrppāṉ</l>
<l>tērokka vūrntāy ceḻuntār vicayaṟkāyk</l>
<l>kārokku mēṉik karumperuṅ kaṇṇaṉē</l>
<l>yārat taḻuvāvan taccōvaccō</l>
<l rend="indent">vāyarkaḷ pōrēṟē yaccōvaccō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Fighting impartially, you drove the chariot with equanimity</l>
<l>for the sake of Vijaya, [wearing] a fresh garland,</l>
<l>in order to end the burdens of this earth.</l>
<l>O He with big, dark eyes [and] a body that resembles a rain cloud!</l>
<l>Having come, embracing [me] fully, Oh! Oh!</l>
<l>Battle bull of the cowherds, Oh! Oh!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
